Sentencas: A composite electrode composed of Pr4Ni3O10 +/-delta-Ce(0.75)Gd(0.1)Pr(0.1)5O(2-delta) (50 wt.%-50 wt.%) was thoroughly investigated in terms of the electrochemical performance as a function of microstructure.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: The electrochemical performance was characterized by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy and the microstructures, characterized by focused ion beam-scanning electron microscopy and 3D reconstructions, were modified by changing the particle size of Pr4Ni3O10 +/-delta and the electrode thickness.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: The distribution of relaxation time method was applied to help resolve electrochemical processes occurring in the electrodes.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: It was found that an appropriate increase in electrode thickness and an appropriate decrease in particle size enhanced the oxygen reduction reaction (ORR) kinetics.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: The lowest area specific resistance obtained in this study at 670 degrees C under pO(2) of 0.21 atm was 0.055 Omega cm(2).
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: Finally, a comparison to the Adler-Lane-Steele (ALS) model was made and the main active site for the ORR was concluded to be triple phase boundaries.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: A fuel cell made of the composite material as the cathode was fabricated and tested.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode

Sentencas: The peak power density was 1 W cm(-2) at 800 degrees C, which demonstrates that this composite material is promising for solid oxide fuel cell cathodes.
Titulo: High performance composite Pr4Ni3O10±δ-Ce0.75Gd0.1Pr0.15O2-δ solid oxide cell air electrode
